data.description: Stunning Lush and Luxurious Alameda with PRIVATE SWIMMING POOL, 2 Car Garage + Golf Garage located in the coveted gated community of Corte Bella Country Club. This magnificent home has been meticulously maintained having a new Carrier Split 3.5 Ton AC and new 12'' R-40 Insulation with finishes that exude sophisticated style.  An impressive entry where your eyes will be drawn to the RESORT REAR YARD and Crown Mouldings in the Living Room and Dining Room which is just off the kitchen making this  an entertainers delight!  In the Kitchen you will find Cherry Cabinetry with Lower Pullouts, Granite Countertops, Center Island, ''Coffee Bar'' Area with Glass Front Cabinet, Under + Upper Cabinet Lighting and 2023 New GE Microwave and Dishwasher. Cornered Family Room with Entertainment Wall, Upgraded Lighting, and Door Wall that exits to the large Covered Patio. You will also find NO shortage of storage space having a large laundry room with cabinetry, Neil's Cabinets in Garage and the multiple added cabinetries by Cozy Factory/Classy Closets built-in the Golf Garage, Master, and Secondary Guest Room. Making your way to the Wing that has the Guest Bedrooms, you first will find a Large Den Space with Built-in Bookcases that is light and bright and overlooks the front entryway and a Powder Room. Going down the hallway is 2  Guests Rooms that share a Large Full Hall Bathroom, which guests will feel they have their own ensuite.   Split floor plan allows for a Private Master Retreat with Large Walk-in Closets, Private Shower, Jacuzzi Tub, His and Her Dual Sinks and Private Door that exits to the Rear Yard. The resort rear yard has a Covered Patio with Sun/Wind Sunshades, Built-in BBQ, just a great space to either relax by the sparkling pool, that has been updated in 2022 or entertain with extended space on the paved sitting areas.  This Alameda has been a great home for the Sellers and the time has come to share this home with someone new! It is one of Corte Bella's Finest.
